car-color-detection/
│── data/
│   ├── train/         # training images (organized by color folders)
│   ├── val/           # validation images (organized by color folders)
│── models/
│   └── car_color_model.h5   # saved trained model
│── gui.py             # Tkinter GUI to preview results
│── train.py           # script to train the CNN model
│── detect.py          # script to run detection (cars + people + rectangles)
│── requirements.txt   # dependencies
│── README.md          # project documentation
